TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT TQ.HVST_ID, TQ.RPT_ID, TM.CORP_CD, R.RPT_TYP_CD, H.HRCY_TYP_CD, TQ.DISCNT_RUN_MODE_CD, TQ.CREATE_TS, TQ.VER_SEQ_NB, TQ.INV_SEQ_NB, TQ.RPT_ADHOC_STAT_CD , ADM.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD AS HVST_ADM_DP_TRM_CD, ADM.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD AS HVST_ADM_DP_TYP_CD, BAS.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD AS HVST_BAS_DP_TRM_CD, BAS.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD AS HVST_BAS_DP_TYP_CD, CNT.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD AS HVST_CNT_DP_TRM_CD, CNT.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD AS HVST_CNT_DP_TYP_CD, FRM.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD AS HVST_FRM_DP_TRM_CD, FRM.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD AS HVST_FRM_DP_TYP_CD, PRF.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD AS HVST_PRF_DP_TRM_CD, PRF.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD AS HVST_PRF_DP_TYP_CD, TQ.LAST_HVST_TS, TQ.SEG_CD, TL.MSTR_CPSL_GID, TQ.OOB_CD, TQ.PERIOD_ID, TQ.CREATE_USER_ID, TQ.UPDT_TS AS UPDT_TS, PRP.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD AS HVST_PRP_DP_TRM_CD, PRP.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD AS HVST_PRP_DP_TYP_CD, --Added as part of ITPR006540 Price Protection (12/04/2014) ADM.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS HVST_ADM_DP_GRP_CD, BAS.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS HVST_BAS_DP_GRP_CD, CNT.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS HVST_CNT_DP_GRP_CD, FRM.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS HVST_FRM_DP_GRP_CD, PRF.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS HVST_PRF_DP_GRP_CD, PRP.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS HVST_PRP_DP_GRP_CD
FROM VRAP.THARVEST_QUE TQ LEFT JOIN VRAP.TCPSL_LOG TL ON TQ.CPSL_GID=TL.CPSL_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.VREPORT R ON TQ.RPT_ID = R.RPT_ID LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP ADM ON R.RPT_ID=ADM.RPT_ID AND ADM.REV_TYP_CD=1 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP BAS ON R.RPT_ID=BAS.RPT_ID AND BAS.REV_TYP_CD=2 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP CNT ON R.RPT_ID=CNT.RPT_ID AND CNT.REV_TYP_CD=4 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP FRM ON R.RPT_ID=FRM.RPT_ID AND FRM.REV_TYP_CD=3 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP PRF ON R.RPT_ID=PRF.RPT_ID AND PRF.REV_TYP_CD=5 INNER JOIN VRAP.THIERARCHY H ON R.HRCY_ID=H.HRCY_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TM ON R.MODEL_TYP_CD = TM.MODEL_TYP_CD LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP PRP ON R.RPT_ID=PRP.RPT_ID AND PRP.REV_TYP_CD=6
WHERE TQ.UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS') AND TQ.HVST_STAT_CD=2 WITH UR
